{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:51:04.985Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_end","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Discovering Key Mock Data**\n\nI've pinpointed the `lib/mock-data-model.ts` file as the central hub for the models and datasets. This is where all the mock data resides! My current focus is figuring out how we can query and repurpose these exact datasets for our needs. I'm starting by listing the available datasets. For instance, there's `previewClientAccounts`, a ClientAccount array.\n\n\n**Enumerating Rich Datasets**\n\nI've made significant progress by thoroughly cataloging the available datasets within `lib/mock-data-model.ts`. Specifically, I've listed each dataset along with its associated data structure, such as `previewProjects` (Project[]), and I also noted the presence of Apex Sovereign, Global Retail and others. The richness and coherency of these models is exciting, and I am leaning towards using this existing file as a central data source.\n\n\n**Designing Dashboard Elements**\n\nI'm now designing the dashboard elements around those key models. For the Clients Overview, I will read and display `previewClientAccounts`, pulling details like Name, Tier, Status, Region, and Compliance Level. I can easily calculate active projects using either the `getProjectsForClient(client.id).length` function or filtering the `previewProjects`. Similarly, for Active Projects, I will directly use `previewProjects`, including details like the enclave type, number of nodes, and status, and adding calibration actions. I will pull data from `previewAgentOperations` or `previewAgentHealths` for the AI Operations Overview.\n\n\n**Integrating Data into Views**\n\nI'm now integrating the data into views. I'm focusing on \"Pending Support Tickets\", and thinking how I can query `previewSupportTickets`. I can display each ticket's ID, Priority, SLA deadline, and subject, and add \"Acknowledge\" and \"Reply Wire\" buttons for the admin, which is great. Also, I'm thinking of displaying `previewInvoices` in \"Billing Status\". I can show details like Invoice ID, Period/Block, Amount, and Status (\"paid\", \"unpaid\"), with the ability to sign and verify them. Lastly, I will be leveraging `previewGovernanceItems` and `previewApprovals` to list compliance alerts and approval requests for \"Governance Alerts / Controls\".\n\n\n**Synchronizing Views Meticulously**\n\nI'm now focused on perfect synchronization with the existing `/admin/clients` and `/admin/projects` views, as well as the portal's client views. This holistic approach, consistent with best practices from a senior Figma designer and frontend engineer, will enhance the app's premium feel. I am checking `app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` again, and considering how my Bento Dashboard will relate to the existing `OversightDeckTab` component. My goal is a superior, tailored dashboard design.\n\n\n**Defining the Command Console**\n\nI'm now writing a detailed internal design plan for the new `app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` file, envisioning it as a command console for Dr. Sarah Vance. I've outlined the page narrative, emphasizing the need for quick, actionable insights on global deployment, compliance, and client accounts, all within a 5-second timeframe. Next, I'm designing the visual metaphor, referencing a high-end, military or financial-grade operations cockpit with a dark theme and glowing cyan accents.\n\n\n**Visualizing Advanced Metrics**\n\nI'm now detailing visual elements, focusing on representing real-time data elegantly. I'm exploring representing cryptographic tokens with hex sequences and simulating telemetry flows with clean vector graphs. I'll maintain a consistent aesthetic with a dark theme and glowing cyan accents.\n\n\n**Constructing Data-Driven Grids**\n\nI'm now designing dashboard grids. My focus is the interactive agent workload lattice (displaying memory and CPU states) and the financial ledger with invoice tokens. I've also detailed the pending SLA support wires and the internal operations command console, each with interactive elements, all within the \"Dr. Vance\" theme. I'm focusing on authentic visual loading states.\n\n\n**Implementing Interactive Visuals**\n\nI'm now implementing interactive visuals. I'm focusing on \"Resolve Alarm\" transitions, which will resolve an alert with a checkmark and green glow, and will post to a live terminal trace. I'm also thinking about hover micro-interactions, such as cursor effects, glowing button borders, and clear highlighting in lists. Next, I'm working on responsive design and mobile strategy, ensuring smooth wrapping on small screens, grid adjustments, responsive padding, and accessible touch regions. Finally, I'm verifying the required imports and am double checking the necessary Lucide icons.\n\n\n**Simulating Terminal Commands**\n\nI'm now diving into the `/app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` file to design the terminal commands simulation, leveraging `useState` for terminal logs and `terminalRunning` for operational status. I'm focusing on crafting an immersive, interactive experience with realistic telemetry streams. I'm keeping a very high standard for design polish, interactivity, and bug-free operation.\n\n\n**Simulating Operational Flows**\n\nI'm now implementing the `runCommand` function, aiming for highly interactive command simulation. I'm focusing on crafting realistic telemetry streams and prioritizing a responsive, immersive experience. I've double-checked that `/app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx` is sufficient for the build and I'm outlining the file structure to optimize the implementation. My plan is for a clean, efficient design.\n\n\n"}}
{"ts":"2026-06-27T06:51:04.989Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"tool","toolName":"editor","toolCallId":"56s72tjf","input":{"path":"/Users/ayushbansal/Documents/GitHub/hirezapp_landing_page/app/admin/dashboard/page.tsx","new_text":"\"use client\";\n\nimport React, { useState, useEffect } from \"react\";\nimport { \n  Activity, Shield, Users, Layers, Bot, MessageSquare, CreditCard, \n  ShieldCheck, History, Settings, Search, ArrowUpRight, Check, \n  AlertCircle, RefreshCw, Cpu, Server, Clock, Lock, CheckCircle, \n  ChevronRight, Terminal, HelpCircle, ExternalLink, Zap, Key, Eye, X, CornerDownRight, Play\n} from \"lucide-react\";\nimport Link from \"next/link\";\nimport { \n  previewClientAccounts, \n  previewProjects, \n  previewAgentOperations, \n  previewAgentHealths,\n  previewSupportTickets, \n  previewInvoices, \n  previewGovernanceItems,\n  previewNotifications,\n  ClientAccount,\n  Project,\n  AgentOperation,\n  SupportTicket,\n  Invoice,\n  GovernanceItem\n} from \"@/lib/mock-data-model\";\nimport { PrivatePageHeader } from \"@/components/private-app\";\n\nexport default function AdminDashboardPage() {\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 1. STATE INITIALIZATION\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // Search & Filter state for Clients\n  const [searchQuery, setSearchQuery] = useState(\"\");\n  \n  // Interactive client detail modal/drawer\n  const [selectedClient, setSelectedClient] = useState<ClientAccount | null>(null);\n  \n  // Simulated support ticket SLA countdowns & active list state\n  const [tickets, setTickets] = useState<SupportTicket[]>(\n    previewSupportTickets.filter(t => t.status !== \"resolved\")\n  );\n  const [acknowledgedTickets, setAcknowledgedTickets] = useState<Record<string, boolean>>({});\n\n  // Governance Alerts state (for resolving mock compliance anomalies)\n  const [govItems, setGovItems] = useState<GovernanceItem[]>(\n    previewGovernanceItems.map((item, idx) => {\n      // Artificially make some items warnings for beautiful operational feedback\n      if (idx === 1) return { ...item, status: \"warning\" as const };\n      if (idx === 3) return { ...item, status: \"non_compliant\" as const };\n      return item;\n    })\n  );\n  const [resolvedGovAlerts, setResolvedGovAlerts] = useState<Record<string, boolean>>({});\n\n  // AI Operations parameter states\n  const [selectedModel, setSelectedModel] = useState<string>(\"GFF-Llama-70B-Gov\");\n  const [modelTemperature, setModelTemperature] = useState<number>(0.15);\n  const [gpuLoadPercent, setGpuLoadPercent] = useState<number>(78);\n  const [isPurgingMemory, setIsPurgingMemory] = useState(false);\n  const [isCalibratingModel, setIsCalibratingModel] = useState(false);\n\n  // Command Console terminal stream state\n  const [terminalLogs, setTerminalLogs] = useState<string[]>([\n    \"SECURE DECK: Multi-enclave telemetry stream connected via TLS 1.3 socket.\",\n    \"eBPF KERNEL: Continuous compliance tracking active on 18 sandbox nodes.\",\n    \"AWAITING DECK COMMANDS: System idle...\"\n  ]);\n  const [isTerminalRunning, setIsTerminalRunning] = useState(false);\n\n  // Success toast message states\n  const [toastMessage, setToastMessage] = useState<string | null>(null);\n\n  const triggerToast = (msg: string) => {\n    setToastMessage(msg);\n    setTimeout(() => setToastMessage(null), 4000);\n  };\n\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // 2. INTERACTIVE ACTIONS (COMMAND EXECUTIONS)\n  // ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n  // Simulated terminal typing effect\n  const appendTerminalLogs = (newLogs: string[], delay: number = 600) => {\n    setIsTerminalRunning(true);\n    let currentLogIndex = 0;\n    \n    const interval = setInterval(() => {\n      if (currentLogIndex < newLogs.length) {\n        setTerminalLogs(prev => [...prev, newLogs[currentLogIndex]]);\n        currentLogIndex++;\n      } else {\n        clearInterval(interval);\n        setIsTerminalRunning(false);\n      }\n    }, delay);\n  };\n\n  // Trigger: Run Diagnostic Scan\n  const handleRunDiagnostic = () => {\n    if (isTerminalRunning) return;\n    setTerminalLogs([\n      \"COMMAND RECEIVED: Trigger diagnostic probe...\",\n      \"TARGET: All isolated enterprise sandboxes (Intel SGX, AMD SEV-SNP, AWS Nitro)\"\n    ]);\n    appendTerminalLogs([\n      \"[PROBE] Scanning client Sovereign Retail Group (client-001)... OK [Verified]\",\n      \"[PROBE] Scanning client National Health Enclave (client-003)... WARN [Thread load high]\",\n      \"[PROBE] Reading eBPF event stream... Compliance rating calculated: 98.42%\",\n      \"[PROBE] System signature checks: SHA-256 certificate validation PASSED.\",\n      \"DIAGNOSTIC STATUS: Operational check completed. Fleet state is stable.\"\n    ], 500);\n    triggerToast(\"Fleet-wide diagnostic probe run successfully.\");\n  };\n\n  // Trigger: Deploy New Enclave Sandbox\n  const handleDeployEnclave = () => {\n    if (isTerminalRunning) return;\n    setTerminalLogs([\n      \"COMMAND RECEIVED: Spin up ephemeral sandbox namespaces...\",\n      \"SECURITY COMPLIANCE: Initiating zero-trust handshake...\"\n    ]);\n    appendTerminalLogs([\n      \"[HSM] Requesting hardware security module (HSM) core key signing...\",\n      \"[SGX] Provisioning Intel SGX secure memory block (256MB PRM)...\",\n      \"[ISO] Locking file namespace in sandboxed micro-OS...\",\n      \"[NET] Creating TLS 1.3 dual-layer socket loop...\",\n      \"[DEPLOY] Enclave cluster deployed successfully: Node CLUSTER-GFF-099 [Active]\",\n      \"DIAGNOSTIC STATUS: Sandbox namespace isolated and active.\"\n    ], 600);\n    triggerToast(\"Ephemeral sandbox container successfully deployed.\");\n  };\n\n  // Trigger: Emergency Lockout Enclaves\n  const handleEmergencyLockout = () => {\n    if (isTerminalRunning) return;\n    setTerminalLogs([\n      \"⚠️ ALERT: EXECUTING FLEET-WIDE SHIELD PROTOCOLS...\",\n      \"AUTHORIZATION REQUIRED: Dr. Sarah Vance - CLEARANCE LEVEL V verified.\"\n    ]);\n    appendTerminalLogs([\n      \"[SHIELD] Decoupling unstable sandbox layers...\",\n      \"[SHIELD] Isolating HSM root keys inside hardware vault...\",\n      \"[SHIELD] Severing external API routing channels...\",\n      \"[SHIELD] Entering localized read-only diagnostic state...\",\n      \"⚠️ STATUS: Fleet-wide secure lockout successfully implemented. Manual recovery required.\"\n    ], 400);\n    triggerToast(\"Emergency lockout implemented. Sandboxes decoupled.\");\n  };\n\n  // Action: Purge agent context cache\n  const handlePurgeMemory = () => {\n    setIsPurgingMemory(true);\n    triggerToast(\"Purging AI agent context allocations...\");\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setIsPurgingMemory(false);\n      setGpuLoadPercent(42);\n      setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n        ...prev,\n        `[gff-ops] Agent ${selectedModel} memory context successfully purged and garbage collected. GPU load reduced to 42%.`\n      ]);\n      triggerToast(\"AI Agent context memory successfully cleared.\");\n    }, 1800);\n  };\n\n  // Action: Calibrate GPU/Model Parameters\n  const handleCalibrateModel = () => {\n    setIsCalibratingModel(true);\n    triggerToast(`Calibrating model lattice weights for ${selectedModel}...`);\n    setTimeout(() => {\n      setIsCalibratingModel(false);\n      setModelTemperature(0.00);\n      setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n        ...prev,\n        `[gff-ops] Recalibrated ${selectedModel} weights. Set deterministic temperature line = 0.00.`\n      ]);\n      triggerToast(\"Model parameters successfully aligned.\");\n    }, 1500);\n  };\n\n  // Action: Acknowledge support wire SLA\n  const handleAcknowledgeTicket = (ticketId: string) => {\n    setAcknowledgedTickets(prev => ({ ...prev, [ticketId]: true }));\n    setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n      ...prev,\n      `[SLA-LEDGER] Ticket wire ${ticketId} acknowledged. Assigned primary core engineer to investigation thread.`\n    ]);\n    triggerToast(`SLA ticket wire ${ticketId} acknowledged.`);\n  };\n\n  // Action: Resolve governance alert override\n  const handleResolveGovAlert = (id: string, name: string) => {\n    setResolvedGovAlerts(prev => ({ ...prev, [id]: true }));\n    setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n      ...prev,\n      `[GOVERNANCE] Policy check anomaly \"${name}\" manually audited and override approved.`\n    ]);\n    triggerToast(`Resolved compliance anomaly: ${name}`);\n  };\n\n  // Filter clients based on search query\n  const filteredClients = previewClientAccounts.filter(c => \n    c.name.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) ||\n    c.region.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase()) ||\n    c.tier.toLowerCase().includes(searchQuery.toLowerCase())\n  );\n\n  return (\n    <div className=\"space-y-6 select-none relative\">\n      {/* Toast Notification */}\n      {toastMessage && (\n        <div className=\"fixed top-12 right-6 z-50 p-4 rounded-xl border border-sky-500/20 bg-black/90 backdrop-blur-md shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)] flex items-center gap-3 animate-[slideIn_0.3s_ease-out]\">\n          <div className=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n          <span className=\"text-[11px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">{toastMessage}</span>\n        </div>\n      )}\n\n      {/* PRIVATE HEADER */}\n      <PrivatePageHeader \n        title=\"OVERSIGHT AND DELIVERY PORTAL\" \n        desc=\"Centralized delivery deck for verifying hardware isolated namespaces, continuous ISO-27001 auditing, and secure support streams.\"\n        actions={\n          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n            <button \n              onClick={handleRunDiagnostic}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.01] text-[11.5px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white hover:bg-white/[0.03] active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center gap-1.5 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            >\n              <RefreshCw className={`w-3.5 h-3.5 ${isTerminalRunning ? \"animate-spin\" : \"\"}`} />\n              <span>Diagnostic Core</span>\n            </button>\n            <button \n              onClick={handleDeployEnclave}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-9 px-4 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[11.5px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-white flex items-center gap-1.5 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(0,157,255,0.25)]\"\n            >\n              <span>Provision Enclave</span>\n              <ArrowUpRight className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        }\n      />\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          TOP KPI TILES (HIGH DENSITY STRIP)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-5\">\n        {/* KPI 1 */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Global Sandboxes</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">{previewClientAccounts.length} Clusters</div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-mono leading-none\">\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-emerald-400\">+100% ONLINE</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400\">\n            <Server className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* KPI 2 */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">eBPF Telemetry</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">48 Core Loops</div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-mono leading-none\">\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-sky-400\">14.2ms Latency</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-3 rounded-lg bg-sky-500/5 border border-sky-500/10 text-[#009DFF]\">\n            <Activity className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* KPI 3 */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">Active SLA Wires</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">\n              {tickets.filter(t => !acknowledgedTickets[t.id]).length} Tickets\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-mono leading-none\">\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-[#E4000F] uppercase\">Critical Countdown</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-3 rounded-lg bg-red-500/5 border border-red-500/10 text-red-400 animate-pulse\">\n            <HelpCircle className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* KPI 4 */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 hover:border-white/10 transition-all flex items-center justify-between\">\n          <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-white/35 uppercase block\">ISO Compliance</span>\n            <div className=\"text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white\">100.0% SECURE</div>\n            <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-mono leading-none\">\n              <span className=\"font-bold text-emerald-400\">0 Breaches</span>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n          <div className=\"p-3 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/5 border border-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400\">\n            <ShieldCheck className=\"w-5 h-5\" />\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          BENTO CORE SYSTEM\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        {/* =========================================================================\n            BENTO CARD 1: CLIENTS OVERVIEW & ACTIVE PROJECTS (LEFT 2/3 COLUMN)\n            ========================================================================= */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 space-y-6\">\n          <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-6\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                  <span className=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[#009DFF] animate-pulse\" />\n                  <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Enterprise Clients Overview</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40\">Secure hardware sandboxes, isolation types, and node telemetry tracking.</p>\n              </div>\n              \n              {/* Search filter input */}\n              <div className=\"relative\">\n                <Search className=\"absolute left-3 top-2.5 w-3.5 h-3.5 text-white/35\" />\n                <input \n                  type=\"text\" \n                  placeholder=\"Search Enclaves...\"\n                  value={searchQuery}\n                  onChange={(e) => setSearchQuery(e.target.value)}\n                  className=\"w-full sm:w-60 h-8.5 pl-9 pr-4 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-black/40 text-[11.5px] font-mono text-white placeholder-white/30 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#009DFF]/30 transition-colors\"\n                />\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Clients Telemetry Grid */}\n            <div className=\"overflow-x-auto\">\n              <table className=\"w-full text-left text-xs font-mono border-collapse\">\n                <thead>\n                  <tr className=\"border-b border-white/5 text-[10px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold\">\n                    <th className=\"pb-3 pr-2\">Enterprise client</th>\n                    <th className=\"pb-3 px-2\">Sandboxes</th>\n                    <th className=\"pb-3 px-2\">Compliance tier</th>\n                    <th className=\"pb-3 px-2\">Sovereign region</th>\n                    <th className=\"pb-3 pl-2 text-right\">Oversight</th>\n                  </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody className=\"divide-y divide-white/[0.02]\">\n                  {filteredClients.map((client) => {\n                    const activeProjsCount = previewProjects.filter(p => p.clientAccountId === client.id).length;\n                    \n                    return (\n                      <tr key={client.id} className=\"group hover:bg-white/[0.01] transition-colors\">\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 pr-2\">\n                          <div className=\"font-bold text-white group-hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-colors text-[12px]\">{client.name}</div>\n                          <div className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35 mt-0.5\">{client.domain}</div>\n                        </td>\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-2\">\n                          <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                            <span className=\"inline-flex h-4 w-4 items-center justify-center rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 border border-[#009DFF]/10 text-[10px] font-bold text-[#009DFF]\">\n                              {activeProjsCount}\n                            </span>\n                            <span className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50\">Active</span>\n                          </div>\n                        </td>\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-2\">\n                          <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-sm px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[9px] font-extrabold uppercase border ${\n                            client.tier === \"Sovereign\" \n                              ? \"bg-purple-500/10 text-purple-400 border-purple-500/20\"\n                              : \"bg-sky-500/10 text-[#009DFF] border-sky-500/20\"\n                          }`}>\n                            {client.tier}\n                          </span>\n                        </td>\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 px-2\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[10.5px] text-white/60\">{client.region}</span>\n                        </td>\n                        <td className=\"py-3.5 pl-2 text-right\">\n                          <button\n                            onClick={() => setSelectedClient(client)}\n                            className=\"h-7 px-2.5 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-[#009DFF]/10 hover:border-[#009DFF]/25 hover:text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-mono text-white/60 transition-all flex items-center gap-1 ml-auto cursor-pointer\"\n                          >\n                            <Eye className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                            <span>Inspect</span>\n                          </button>\n                        </td>\n                      </tr>\n                    );\n                  })}\n                  {filteredClients.length === 0 && (\n                    <tr>\n                      <td colSpan={5} className=\"py-8 text-center text-white/30 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                        No isolated enterprise clients resolved on telemetry scan.\n                      </td>\n                    </tr>\n                  )}\n                </tbody>\n              </table>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Nested Section: Active Projects Layer */}\n            <div className=\"pt-6 border-t border-white/5 space-y-4\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                  <h4 className=\"text-[11.5px] font-bold font-mono tracking-widest text-white uppercase\">Active Sandbox Projects (Global Lattice)</h4>\n                  <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/35\">Running isolated eBPF calibrated virtual systems.</p>\n                </div>\n                <Link \n                  href=\"/admin/projects\"\n                  className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\"\n                >\n                  <span>Global Projects List</span>\n                  <ChevronRight className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n                </Link>\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n                {previewProjects.slice(0, 4).map((proj) => {\n                  const clientObj = previewClientAccounts.find(c => c.id === proj.clientAccountId);\n                  \n                  return (\n                    <div \n                      key={proj.id}\n                      className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/20 hover:border-white/10 transition-all space-y-3\"\n                    >\n                      <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between\">\n                        <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                          <span className=\"text-[8.5px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase\">\n                            {proj.id}\n                          </span>\n                          <h5 className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white uppercase truncate max-w-[200px]\">{proj.name}</h5>\n                          <p className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 truncate max-w-[200px]\">Client: {clientObj?.name || \"GFF Tenant\"}</p>\n                        </div>\n                        <span className={`inline-flex items-center gap-1 rounded-sm px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[8.5px] font-mono font-bold uppercase border ${\n                          proj.status === \"active\" \n                            ? \"bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border-emerald-500/20\"\n                            : proj.status === \"evaluating\"\n                            ? \"bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border-amber-500/20\"\n                            : \"bg-white/5 text-white/40 border-white/10\"\n                        }`}>\n                          {proj.status}\n                        </span>\n                      </div>\n\n                      <div className=\"pt-2 border-t border-white/5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-[9px] text-white/40 font-mono\">\n                        <div>Enclave: <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">{proj.enclaveType}</span></div>\n                        <div className=\"text-right\">Active Nodes: <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">{proj.nodesCount}</span></div>\n                      </div>\n                    </div>\n                  );\n                })}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* =========================================================================\n              BENTO CARD 3: SOVEREIGN MULTI-AGENT AI OPERATIONS (LEFT 2/3 COLUMN - ROW 2)\n              ========================================================================= */}\n          <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-6\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                  <Bot className=\"w-4 h-4 text-purple-400\" />\n                  <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Sovereign Multi-Agent AI Operations</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40\">Calibrate neural loop parameters and isolate volatile thread caches.</p>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Model Selector Tabs */}\n              <div className=\"flex bg-black/40 rounded-lg p-1 border border-white/5\">\n                {[\"GFF-Llama-70B-Gov\", \"GFF-Agent-Coder-v4\", \"Sovereign-Reasoning-v1\"].map((model) => (\n                  <button\n                    key={model}\n                    onClick={() => {\n                      setSelectedModel(model);\n                      // Deterministally shift weights to simulate real agent inspection\n                      if (model === \"GFF-Llama-70B-Gov\") {\n                        setModelTemperature(0.15);\n                        setGpuLoadPercent(78);\n                      } else if (model === \"GFF-Agent-Coder-v4\") {\n                        setModelTemperature(0.20);\n                        setGpuLoadPercent(44);\n                      } else {\n                        setModelTemperature(0.00);\n                        setGpuLoadPercent(91);\n                      }\n                    }}\n                    className={`px-2.5 py-1.5 rounded-md text-[9px] font-mono tracking-wider font-bold uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer ${\n                      selectedModel === model \n                        ? \"bg-[#009DFF] text-white shadow-md\" \n                        : \"text-white/40 hover:text-white\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    {model.split(\"-\")[1]}\n                  </button>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* High-density active operations overview metrics */}\n            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5\">\n              \n              {/* Telemetry Panel */}\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/20 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase block tracking-wider font-bold\">Dynamic Allocation</span>\n                <div className=\"space-y-2.5\">\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[11px]\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/55\">Inference Temp:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">{modelTemperature.toFixed(2)}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[11px]\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/55\">Active Loops:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">12 Threads</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[11px]\">\n                    <span className=\"text-white/55\">Active Memory:</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-white font-bold\">6.2 GB / 8.0 GB</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Progress Slider Display (Context/GPU utilization) */}\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/20 space-y-3 font-mono\">\n                <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">GPU Load Index</span>\n                  <span className={`text-[10px] font-bold ${gpuLoadPercent > 85 ? \"text-rose-400 animate-pulse\" : \"text-[#009DFF]\"}`}>{gpuLoadPercent}%</span>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"h-1.5 w-full bg-black/40 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-white/5 p-[1px]\">\n                  <div \n                    className=\"h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#009DFF] to-cyan-400 rounded-full transition-all duration-500\"\n                    style={{ width: `${gpuLoadPercent}%` }}\n                  />\n                </div>\n                <span className=\"text-[8.5px] text-white/20 block leading-tight uppercase\">Isolated eBPF Sandbox Namespace Memory Limit</span>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Command Actions Panel for Agent */}\n              <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/20 flex flex-col justify-between gap-3 font-mono\">\n                <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold\">Isolate Actions</span>\n                <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2\">\n                  <button\n                    onClick={handlePurgeMemory}\n                    disabled={isPurgingMemory}\n                    className=\"h-8 rounded border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center disabled:opacity-40\"\n                  >\n                    {isPurgingMemory ? (\n                      <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 animate-spin text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                    ) : (\n                      <span>Purge Cache</span>\n                    )}\n                  </button>\n                  <button\n                    onClick={handleCalibrateModel}\n                    disabled={isCalibratingModel}\n                    className=\"h-8 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase hover:bg-[#009DFF]/20 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center disabled:opacity-40\"\n                  >\n                    {isCalibratingModel ? (\n                      <RefreshCw className=\"w-3 h-3 animate-spin text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                    ) : (\n                      <span>Calibrate</span>\n                    )}\n                  </button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Model Logs Console */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n              <div className=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[9px] font-mono uppercase font-bold text-white/30 tracking-widest\">\n                <span>Model Threading Signal</span>\n                <span className=\"text-emerald-400\">Stable Heartbeat (00:01s)</span>\n              </div>\n              <div className=\"p-3 bg-black/40 border border-white/5 rounded-xl text-[10.5px] font-mono text-white/60 space-y-2 leading-relaxed h-[100px] overflow-y-auto\">\n                <div>[06-27-2026 15:40:11] <span className=\"text-[#00FFC2] font-bold\">[HSM SIGN]</span> Ephemeral public keys matching SHA-256 (0xFF92) validated.</div>\n                <div>[06-27-2026 15:42:04] <span className=\"text-sky-400 font-bold\">[ALIGN]</span> Model context alignment parameters calibration complete. Temperature set.</div>\n                {isPurgingMemory && <div className=\"text-[#009DFF] animate-pulse font-bold\">[OPS COMMAND] Purging volatile memory blocks... Context sync active.</div>}\n                {isCalibratingModel && <div className=\"text-purple-400 animate-pulse font-bold\">[OPS COMMAND] calibrating model lattice weights for GFF-Llama-70B-Gov...</div>}\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* =========================================================================\n            RIGHT COLUMN: GOVERNANCE, BILLING, SUPPORT, COMMAND ACTIONS\n            ========================================================================= */}\n        <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n          \n          {/* =========================================================================\n              BENTO CARD 2: SECURITY GOVERNANCE & CRITICAL ALERTS (RIGHT 1/3)\n              ========================================================================= */}\n          <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <Shield className=\"w-4 h-4 text-red-400 shrink-0\" />\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Governance & Guardrail Alerts</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Verify ISO-27001 rulesets manually.</p>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"h-5 px-1.5 rounded-full bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold text-red-400 flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse\">\n                ALARM\n              </span>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Compliance Alerts list */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n              {govItems.map((item) => {\n                const isResolved = resolvedGovAlerts[item.id];\n                \n                return (\n                  <div \n                    key={item.id} \n                    className={`p-3.5 rounded-xl border transition-all ${\n                      isResolved \n                        ? \"bg-emerald-500/5 border-emerald-500/10 opacity-60\" \n                        : item.status === \"non_compliant\"\n                        ? \"bg-red-500/5 border-red-500/10 shadow-[inset_0_0_15px_rgba(239,68,68,0.02)]\"\n                        : item.status === \"warning\"\n                        ? \"bg-amber-500/5 border-amber-500/15\"\n                        : \"bg-black/10 border-white/5\"\n                    }`}\n                  >\n                    <div className=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n                      <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                          <span className={`h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full ${\n                            isResolved ? \"bg-emerald-500\" :\n                            item.status === \"non_compliant\" ? \"bg-red-500 animate-pulse\" : \"bg-amber-400\"\n                          }`} />\n                          <h4 className=\"text-[11px] font-bold text-white font-mono uppercase\">{item.standard}</h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <p className=\"text-[9.5px] text-white/60 font-mono leading-relaxed\">{item.name}</p>\n                        <span className=\"text-[8px] text-white/30 font-mono block\">Last audited: {item.lastChecked}</span>\n                      </div>\n                      \n                      {!isResolved && (item.status === \"non_compliant\" || item.status === \"warning\") && (\n                        <button\n                          onClick={() => handleResolveGovAlert(item.id, item.name)}\n                          className=\"h-6 px-2 rounded bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-[#009DFF]/30 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/5 hover:text-[#009DFF] text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/60 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center\"\n                        >\n                          Verify\n                        </button>\n                      )}\n\n                      {isResolved && (\n                        <span className=\"text-emerald-400 flex items-center gap-0.5 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold\">\n                          <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                          <span>Audited</span>\n                        </span>\n                      )}\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n                );\n              })}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* =========================================================================\n              BENTO CARD 4: FINANCIAL LEDGER & BILLING TOKENS (RIGHT 1/3)\n              ========================================================================= */}\n          <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n              <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\">\n                  <CreditCard className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                  <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Cryptographic Billing Ledger</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Secure invoice tokens matching compute epochs.</p>\n              </div>\n              <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest\">GFF_FIN</span>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Invoices list */}\n            <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n              {previewInvoices.slice(0, 3).map((invoice) => (\n                <div \n                  key={invoice.id}\n                  className=\"p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/20 hover:border-[#009DFF]/15 transition-all space-y-2 font-mono\"\n                >\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[11px]\">\n                    <span className=\"font-bold text-white uppercase\">{invoice.id}</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-[#009DFF] font-bold\">{invoice.amount}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between text-[9px] text-white/35\">\n                    <span>{invoice.category}</span>\n                    <span>Block: {invoice.dueDate.split(\"-\")[1] || \"#14421\"}</span>\n                  </div>\n                  <div className=\"pt-1.5 border-t border-white/[0.03] flex items-center justify-between text-[8px] text-white/20\">\n                    <span className=\"truncate max-w-[120px] font-bold font-mono\">SEAL: {invoice.hash.substring(0, 16)}...</span>\n                    <span className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold uppercase\">SECURE</span>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n\n            <button \n              onClick={() => {\n                triggerToast(\"Verifying Ledger Block signature tokens... SUCCESS.\");\n                setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n                  ...prev,\n                  \"[HSM-FIN] Cryptographic invoices successfully verified against treasury key ledger: MATCH.\"\n                ]);\n              }}\n              className=\"w-full h-8 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-[#009DFF]/25 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/5 hover:text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white/85 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-1\"\n            >\n              <Key className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              <span>Verify Block Signatures</span>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          BENTO ROW 3: SLA TICKETS + SYSTEM COMMAND CONSOLE\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n        \n        {/* =========================================================================\n            BENTO CARD 5: PENDING SLA SUPPORT WIRES (LEFT 2/3 COLUMN)\n            ========================================================================= */}\n        <div className=\"lg:col-span-2 relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between gap-4 border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n              <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                <MessageSquare className=\"w-4 h-4 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n                <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Pending Support Wires</h3>\n              </div>\n              <p className=\"text-[11px] text-white/40\">Secure priority chat lines with active SLA count-down timers.</p>\n            </div>\n            <Link \n              href=\"/admin/support\"\n              className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] hover:underline flex items-center gap-1\"\n            >\n              <span>Manage SLA Wires</span>\n              <ChevronRight className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n            </Link>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n            {tickets.slice(0, 2).map((ticket) => {\n              const isAck = acknowledgedTickets[ticket.id];\n              \n              return (\n                <div \n                  key={ticket.id}\n                  className={`p-4 rounded-xl border transition-all ${\n                    isAck \n                      ? \"bg-emerald-500/5 border-emerald-500/10 opacity-70\" \n                      : ticket.priority === \"high\" || ticket.priority === \"critical\"\n                      ? \"bg-rose-500/5 border-rose-500/10\" \n                      : \"bg-black/20 border-white/5\"\n                  } space-y-3`}\n                >\n                  <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between\">\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                      <span className={`inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[8px] font-bold font-mono border uppercase ${\n                        ticket.priority === \"high\" || ticket.priority === \"critical\"\n                          ? \"bg-red-500/10 text-red-400 border-red-500/20 animate-pulse\" \n                          : \"bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 border-amber-500/20\"\n                      }`}>\n                        {ticket.priority.toUpperCase()} Priority\n                      </span>\n                      <span className=\"text-[9.5px] font-mono text-white/30\">{ticket.id}</span>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] text-white/50 font-mono\">\n                      <Clock className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5 text-rose-400 animate-pulse\" />\n                      <span>{isAck ? \"ACKNOWLEDGED\" : \"00h:14m:22s\"}</span>\n                    </div>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                    <h4 className=\"text-[11.5px] font-bold text-white uppercase font-mono tracking-wide leading-tight line-clamp-1\">{ticket.title}</h4>\n                    <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/50 font-mono line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed\">{ticket.desc}</p>\n                  </div>\n\n                  <div className=\"pt-2 border-t border-white/5 flex justify-between items-center\">\n                    <span className=\"text-[9.5px] text-[#009DFF] font-mono uppercase font-bold\">GFF CORE SECURE</span>\n                    \n                    {!isAck ? (\n                      <button\n                        onClick={() => handleAcknowledgeTicket(ticket.id)}\n                        className=\"h-7 px-3 rounded bg-[#009DFF]/10 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/20 text-[#009DFF] border border-[#009DFF]/20 text-[9px] font-mono font-bold uppercase transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center\"\n                      >\n                        Acknowledge\n                      </button>\n                    ) : (\n                      <span className=\"text-emerald-400 text-[9.5px] font-mono font-bold flex items-center gap-0.5\">\n                        <Check className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                        <span>Acknowledge</span>\n                      </span>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              );\n            })}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        {/* =========================================================================\n            BENTO CARD 6: INTERNAL OPERATIONS COMMAND CONSOLE (RIGHT 1/3)\n            ========================================================================= */}\n        <div className=\"relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/40 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 space-y-4\">\n          <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 pb-3\">\n            <h3 className=\"text-xs font-bold font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white\">Internal Operations Command Console</h3>\n            <p className=\"text-[10px] text-white/40\">Trigger secure sandboxed system overrides.</p>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Console commands list */}\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 font-mono\">\n            <button \n              onClick={handleRunDiagnostic}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-10 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            >\n              <Zap className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#009DFF]\" />\n              <span>Probe Fleet</span>\n            </button>\n            <button \n              onClick={handleDeployEnclave}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-10 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white/80 hover:text-white transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            >\n              <Server className=\"w-3 h-3 text-emerald-400\" />\n              <span>Provision Node</span>\n            </button>\n            <button \n              onClick={() => {\n                if (isTerminalRunning) return;\n                setTerminalLogs([\n                  \"COMMAND RECEIVED: Flush compliance auditing ledgers...\",\n                  \"TARGET: ISO-27001 continuous audit trail namespace.\"\n                ]);\n                appendTerminalLogs([\n                  \"[AUDIT] Reading compliance audit files list...\",\n                  \"[AUDIT] Generating cryptographical SHA-256 signatures...\",\n                  \"[AUDIT] Zipping signed audit trail... SHA_0xBB99 verified.\",\n                  \"DIAGNOSTIC STATUS: Compliance audit log sealed and locked.\"\n                ], 500);\n                triggerToast(\"Compliance audit logs cryptographically compiled.\");\n              }}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-10 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-[#009DFF]/5 hover:border-[#009DFF]/20 text-white/80 hover:text-[#009DFF] transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            >\n              <ShieldCheck className=\"w-3 h-3 text-purple-400\" />\n              <span>Seal Audits</span>\n            </button>\n            <button \n              onClick={handleEmergencyLockout}\n              disabled={isTerminalRunning}\n              className=\"h-10 text-[9px] font-bold uppercase rounded-lg border border-[#E4000F]/20 bg-[#E4000F]/5 text-red-400 hover:bg-[#E4000F]/15 hover:border-[#E4000F]/40 transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center gap-1 disabled:opacity-40\"\n            >\n              <Lock className=\"w-3 h-3\" />\n              <span>Lockdown</span>\n            </button>\n          </div>\n\n          {/* Interactive Shell Output Console */}\n          <div className=\"space-y-1.5 font-mono\">\n            <span className=\"text-[8px] text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest font-bold block\">Telemetry Diagnostic Logs</span>\n            <div className=\"p-3 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-900 rounded-xl space-y-1 text-[9.5px] text-zinc-400 h-[100px] overflow-y-auto leading-relaxed scrollbar-thin select-text\">\n              {terminalLogs.map((log, index) => (\n                <div key={index} className=\"flex gap-1.5 items-start\">\n                  <CornerDownRight className=\"w-3 h-3 text-[#009DFF] shrink-0 mt-0.5\" />\n                  <span className={index === terminalLogs.length - 1 && isTerminalRunning ? \"text-[#009DFF] font-bold animate-pulse\" : \"\"}>\n                    {log}\n                  </span>\n                </div>\n              ))}\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      {/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n          6. INTERACTIVE SLIDE-OVER DRAWER (CLIENT INSPECTION)\n          --------------------------------------------------------------------------- */}\n      {selectedClient && (\n        <div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-50 flex justify-end\">\n          {/* Backdrop */}\n          <div \n            onClick={() => setSelectedClient(null)}\n            className=\"absolute inset-0 bg-black/70 backdrop-blur-sm transition-opacity\" \n          />\n          \n          {/* Drawer container */}\n          <div className=\"relative w-full max-w-lg h-full bg-[#030303] border-l border-white/5 p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col justify-between overflow-y-auto z-10 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.8)] animate-[slideLeft_0.3s_ease-out]\">\n            <div className=\"space-y-6\">\n              {/* Drawer Header */}\n              <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4\">\n                <div className=\"space-y-1\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n                    OVERSIGHT DECK TELEMETRY\n                  </span>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-sm font-bold text-white uppercase font-mono tracking-wider\">\n                    {selectedClient.name}\n                  </h3>\n                </div>\n                <button \n                  onClick={() => setSelectedClient(null)}\n                  className=\"h-8 w-8 rounded-full border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01] hover:bg-white/[0.03] text-white flex items-center justify-center transition-all cursor-pointer\"\n                  aria-label=\"Close inspection drawer\"\n                >\n                  <X className=\"w-4 h-4\" />\n                </button>\n              </div>\n\n              {/* Drawer Content */}\n              <div className=\"space-y-6 font-mono text-[11px]\">\n                \n                {/* Section: Isolation Specs */}\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-black/40 space-y-3\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold block\">Sandbox Enclave Profile</span>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-y-2.5\">\n                    <div className=\"text-white/45\">Isolation Mode:</div>\n                    <div className=\"text-white font-bold text-right\">{selectedClient.tier === \"Sovereign\" ? \"Intel SGX (MIL-SPEC)\" : \"AMD SEV-SNP (Isolated)\"}</div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-white/45\">Compliance Status:</div>\n                    <div className=\"text-emerald-400 font-bold text-right\">100% COMPLIANT</div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-white/45\">System Region:</div>\n                    <div className=\"text-white font-bold text-right\">{selectedClient.region}</div>\n\n                    <div className=\"text-white/45\">Compliance Rating:</div>\n                    <div className=\"text-white font-bold text-right\">{selectedClient.complianceLevel}</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Section: Operations Telemetry */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold block\">Virtual Node Instances</span>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"space-y-2\">\n                    {previewProjects.filter(p => p.clientAccountId === selectedClient.id).map(proj => (\n                      <div \n                        key={proj.id}\n                        className=\"p-3 rounded-lg border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/80 flex justify-between items-center\"\n                      >\n                        <div className=\"space-y-0.5\">\n                          <span className=\"text-white font-bold text-[10.5px] block truncate max-w-[200px]\">{proj.name}</span>\n                          <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/30 font-mono\">{proj.id} • {proj.enclaveType}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <span className=\"h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse\" />\n                      </div>\n                    ))}\n                    {previewProjects.filter(p => p.clientAccountId === selectedClient.id).length === 0 && (\n                      <div className=\"p-4 text-center border border-dashed border-white/5 rounded-lg text-white/30 text-[10px]\">\n                        No sandbox nodes provisioned for this tenant.\n                      </div>\n                    )}\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n\n                {/* Section: Security Logs */}\n                <div className=\"space-y-3\">\n                  <span className=\"text-[9px] text-white/35 uppercase tracking-wider font-bold block\">Enclave Handshake Logs</span>\n                  \n                  <div className=\"p-3 bg-zinc-950 border border-zinc-900 rounded-lg text-[10px] text-zinc-400 space-y-1.5 h-[120px] overflow-y-auto leading-relaxed\">\n                    <div>[06-27-2026 15:40:01] HSM certificates received. Matches public key.</div>\n                    <div>[06-27-2026 15:40:05] Kernel verification check: eBPF monitoring active.</div>\n                    <div>[06-27-2026 15:40:08] Double-signed JWT verification complete. SECURE.</div>\n                    <div>[06-27-2026 15:41:22] Volatile sandbox memory garbage collected successfully.</div>\n                  </div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n\n            {/* Drawer Footer Actions */}\n            <div className=\"pt-6 border-t border-white/5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n              <button\n                onClick={() => {\n                  triggerToast(`Triggered diagnostic recalibration for ${selectedClient.name}.`);\n                  setTerminalLogs(prev => [\n                    ...prev,\n                    `[PROBE] Recalibrated eBPF telemetry boundary lines for client ID ${selectedClient.id}.`\n                  ]);\n                }}\n                className=\"h-9 rounded border border-white/10 hover:border-[#009DFF]/30 hover:bg-[#009DFF]/5 hover:text-[#009DFF] text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white transition-all cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-center\"\n              >\n                Recalibrate eBPF\n              </button>\n              <Link\n                href={`/admin/clients`}\n                className=\"h-9 rounded bg-[#009DFF] hover:bg-[#0082d4] text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase text-white transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-1\"\n              >\n                <span>Full Credentials</span>\n                <ExternalLink className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n              </Link>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}"}}}
